{"id": "1197142957518757968", "channel_id": "1196941586446176297", "type": 19, "author_id": "1176579168448823471", "author_name": "llhwwc_89248", "author_bot": false, "content": "相比于我这种独行玩家，这种新手向攻略确实具有很高的实用价值，我也过于从硬核强度方面去考虑了～", "timestamp": "2024-01-17T11:38:42.913000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1181971546496061540"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1197119743820308481", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1196941586446176297", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "角色梯度总榜与分榜（超认真项与整活项）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179734373019748", "1196356931191832677", "1174179755759763526", "1174179680056791130", "1174179700470460447"]}
