{"id": "1197206646288568420", "channel_id": "1197139130182803517", "type": 0, "author_id": "1189791024424431627", "author_name": "vivivispray", "author_bot": false, "content": "当然啦，不同的造物会在不同的场合，不同的机师手里发光，这里排的顺序是考虑到造物的收益和代价，在我看来，越后面的造物代价太高了，而收益也不适用于大部分队伍和环境", "timestamp": "2024-01-17T15:51:47.499000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1197139130182803517", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜造物T度榜", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179680056791130", "1196356931191832677", "1174180524034637854"]}
